text: Malotenkashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Baygildinsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 172 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 29 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 1 km from Baygildino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Malotenkashevo
